<h2 id="steganography">Steganography</h2>

<p><a id="file-steganography"> </a></p>
<h3 id="file-steganography">File Steganography</h3>
<ul>
  <li><code>file</code> to check file type</li>
  <li>Try checking the magic bytes if that doesnâ€™t work</li>
  <li><code>binwalk</code></li>
  <li><code>strings</code></li>
  <li><code>hexdump</code></li>
  <li>exif data</li>
  <li>If it is an image:
    <ul>
      <li>LSB or MSB</li>
      <li>Color filters (Gimp, Photoshop)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>If it is a Microsoft file like Word or Excel
    <ul>
      <li>rename file extension to <code>.zip</code></li>
      <li>unzip files, and analyze from there</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

